gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Bucks 119, 76ers 98
gameRecap.excerpt: The Bucks defeated the 76ers, 119-98. Giannis Antetokounmpo recorded 30 points, 12 rebounds, and nine assists for the Bucks, with Damian Lillard adding 24 points, nine assists, and seven rebounds in the victory. Tyrese Maxey tallied 24 points, seven assists, and three rebounds for the 76ers in the losing effort. The Bucks improve to 37-21, while the 76ers fall to 33-24.
